<!DOCTYPE html>
<html><head><meta charset="utf-8">
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #222; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
  .header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; border-bottom: 3px solid #1e40af; padding-bottom: 12px; margin-bottom: 22px; }
  .header .logo img { max-height: 65px; max-width: 200px; }
  .header .company-info { text-align: right; font-size: 11px; color: #444; }
  .header .company-info .cname { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #1e40af; }
  h1.title { text-align: center; font-size: 18px; text-decoration: underline; margin: 12px 0 20px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
  .confidential { text-align: center; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #dc2626; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .meta { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 18px; font-size: 12px; }
  .to-block { background: #f0f4ff; border-left: 4px solid #1e40af; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 12px; }
  .to-block .label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  p { margin: 8px 0; text-align: justify; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 12px 0; }
  th, td { border: 1px solid #d1d5db; padding: 7px 10px; font-size: 12px; }
  th { background: #1e40af; color: #fff; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; }
  tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #f8fafc; }
  .compare-table th.old { background: #6b7280; }
  .compare-table th.new { background: #059669; }
  .compare-table td.highlight { font-weight: 700; color: #059669; }
  .badge-inc { display: inline-block; background: #d1fae5; color: #065f46; font-weight: 700; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 11px; }
  .badge-type { display: inline-block; background: #dbeafe; color: #1e40af; font-weight: 700; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 11px; }
  .summary-box { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin: 16px 0; }
  .summary-item { flex: 1; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 6px; }
  .summary-item .s-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: 0.75; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .summary-item .s-val { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 800; }
  .s-old { background: #f3f4f6; color: #374151; }
  .s-new { background: #d1fae5; color: #065f46; }
  .s-inc { background: #dbeafe; color: #1e40af; }
  .breakdown-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin: 14px 0 6px; color: #374151; }
  .signature-block { margin-top: 45px; display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; }
  .sig-inner { text-align: center; min-width: 180px; }
  .sig-inner img { max-height: 55px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .sig-inner .sig-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px; }
  .sig-inner .sig-title { font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280; }
  .footer { margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; padding-top: 6px; text-align: center; font-size: 10px; color: #9ca3af; }
  .doc-ref { font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280; }
</style>
</head><body>

<!-- Header -->
<div class="header">
  <div class="logo">
    {{#if company.logo_url}}<img src="{{company.logo_url}}" />{{else}}<div style="font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#1e40af">{{company.name}}</div>{{/if}}
  </div>
  <div class="company-info">
    <div class="cname">{{company.name}}</div>
    <div>{{company.address}}{{#if company.city}}, {{company.city}}{{/if}}{{#if company.state}}, {{company.state}}{{/if}} {{company.pincode}}</div>
    <div>{{company.email}} | {{company.phone}}</div>
    {{#if company.website}}<div>{{company.website}}</div>{{/if}}
    {{#if company.gstin}}<div>GSTIN: {{company.gstin}}</div>{{/if}}
  </div>
</div>

<div class="confidential">— CONFIDENTIAL —</div>
<h1 class="title">Salary Revision / Increment Letter</h1>

<!-- Doc Ref & Date -->
<div class="meta">
  <div class="doc-ref">Ref No: <strong>{{doc_number}}</strong></div>
  <div class="doc-ref">Date: <strong>{{data.issue_date}}</strong></div>
</div>

<!-- To Block -->
<div class="to-block">
  <div class="label">To</div>
  <div><strong>{{employee.full_name}}</strong></div>
  <div>{{employee.designation}}{{#if employee.department}} | {{employee.department}}{{/if}}</div>
  {{#if employee.emp_code}}<div>Employee Code: {{employee.emp_code}}</div>{{/if}}
</div>

<p><strong>Subject: Salary Revision effective {{data.increment_date}}</strong></p>

<p>Dear <strong>{{employee.full_name}}</strong>,</p>

<p>
  We are pleased to inform you that the management has decided to revise your salary package
  with effect from <strong>{{data.increment_date}}</strong>, as a recognition of your contribution,
  performance, and dedication to the organisation.
</p>

<!-- Summary boxes -->
<div class="summary-box">
  <div class="summary-item s-old">
    <div class="s-label">Current Annual CTC</div>
    <div class="s-val">₹{{data.current_ctc_fmt}}</div>
  </div>
  <div class="summary-item s-inc">
    <div class="s-label">{{data.increment_label}}</div>
    <div class="s-val">{{data.increment_display}}</div>
  </div>
  <div class="summary-item s-new">
    <div class="s-label">Revised Annual CTC</div>
    <div class="s-val">₹{{data.new_ctc_fmt}}</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- CTC Comparison Table -->
<div class="breakdown-title">CTC Comparison</div>
<table class="compare-table">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Component</th>
      <th class="old">Current Monthly (₹)</th>
      <th class="new">Revised Monthly (₹)</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td>Basic Salary</td><td>{{data.cur_basic_fmt}}</td><td class="highlight">{{data.new_basic_fmt}}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>HRA</td><td>{{data.cur_hra_fmt}}</td><td class="highlight">{{data.new_hra_fmt}}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Dearness Allowance (DA)</td><td>{{data.cur_da_fmt}}</td><td class="highlight">{{data.new_da_fmt}}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Conveyance Allowance</td><td>{{data.cur_conv_fmt}}</td><td class="highlight">{{data.new_conv_fmt}}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Medical Allowance</td><td>{{data.cur_med_fmt}}</td><td class="highlight">{{data.new_med_fmt}}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Special Allowance</td><td>{{data.cur_special_fmt}}</td><td class="highlight">{{data.new_special_fmt}}</td></tr>
    <tr style="background:#f0fdf4;font-weight:700;">
      <td><strong>Gross Monthly Salary</strong></td>
      <td>{{data.cur_gross_fmt}}</td>
      <td class="highlight">{{data.new_gross_fmt}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>PF (Employee — 12% of Basic)</td>
      <td>{{data.cur_pf_fmt}}</td>
      <td class="highlight">{{data.new_pf_fmt}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr style="background:#eff6ff;font-weight:700;">
      <td><strong>Monthly Net Pay (Take-home)</strong></td>
      <td>{{data.cur_net_fmt}}</td>
      <td class="highlight">{{data.new_net_fmt}}</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>
  Your revised salary structure will be effective from <strong>{{data.increment_date}}</strong>.
  The revised compensation package is confidential and you are requested not to disclose
  the same to any other employee or any outside person.
</p>

<p>
  We appreciate your efforts and look forward to your continued contribution to the growth
  of the organisation. Congratulations on your increment!
</p>

<p>Please sign and return a copy of this letter as acknowledgement of the revised terms.</p>

<br/>
<p>Yours sincerely,</p>

<!-- Signature -->
<div class="signature-block">
  <div class="sig-inner">
    {{#if company.signature_url}}<img src="{{company.signature_url}}" />{{/if}}
    {{#if company.stamp_url}}<img src="{{company.stamp_url}}" style="max-height:50px;margin-left:10px;" />{{/if}}
    <div style="border-top: 1px solid #374151; margin-top: 8px; padding-top: 6px;">
      <div class="sig-name">{{company.signatory_name}}</div>
      <div class="sig-title">{{company.signatory_designation}}</div>
      <div class="sig-title">{{company.name}}</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Acknowledgement -->
<div style="margin-top:40px; border:1px dashed #9ca3af; padding:12px; border-radius:6px;">
  <p style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 10px;">ACKNOWLEDGEMENT</p>
  <p style="font-size:11px;margin:0;">
    I, <strong>{{employee.full_name}}</strong>, hereby acknowledge receipt of this salary revision
    letter dated <strong>{{data.issue_date}}</strong> and accept the revised terms effective
    <strong>{{data.increment_date}}</strong>.
  </p>
  <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:24px;font-size:11px;">
    <div>Signature: ___________________________</div>
    <div>Date: ___________________________</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  {{company.name}} | {{company.address}}{{#if company.city}}, {{company.city}}{{/if}} |
  {{company.email}} | {{company.phone}}
  {{#if company.gstin}} | GSTIN: {{company.gstin}}{{/if}}
</div>

</body></html>
